{
  "name": "basalt_preprocess_to_traintest",
  "description": "玄武岩数据预处理流程：从 GEOROC / PetDB 筛选到产出最终训练集/测试集（06_normalize_basalt_{train,test}.csv）。不含模型训练及下游分析。{repo_root} 指向项目根。",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "n1",
      "type": "note",
      "title": "流程说明 / 路径约定",
      "position": { "x": 40, "y": 40 },
      "params": {
        "content": "数据预处理流程：GEOROC/PetDB 规则筛选 → 合并 → 切分 → 全局 RF 插补 + 缺失 mask → 主量无水标准化 → 选择性 SMOTE（仅训练集）→ 分位数分箱归一化 → 最终训练集/测试集。\n\n占位符：{python_exe}=运行 app.py 的解释器；{repo_root}=项目根。脚本路径由 config/paths.py 统一管理；插补/SMOTE/分位数的 fit 仅用训练集（分位数从 SMOTE 前训练集拟合），测试集只 transform（防数据泄露）。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n2",
      "type": "note",
      "title": "输入起点（外部已就位）",
      "position": { "x": 40, "y": 260 },
      "params": {
        "content": "前置输入应已放入 data/：\n- 00_raw/ 原始 GEOROC（含 references_structured.csv）、PetDB 2.0 合并表 petdbv2_merged.csv\n- 01_cm_reclass_input/ 汇聚边缘细分产出（含 basalt_refined_expanded.csv，由独立项目 convergent_margin_reclass 生成，不在本流程内）。\n\n提示：01_preprocessing/filter 下的 *_filter_tuner_gui.py 为可选交互式调参工具，正式筛选入口为 extract_georoc.py / extract_petdb.py。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n3",
      "type": "command_task",
      "title": "1a. GEOROC 筛选（规则固化）",
      "position": { "x": 340, "y": 120 },
      "params": {
        "label": "extract_georoc.py",
        "command": "\"{python_exe}\" \"{repo_root}\\01_preprocessing\\filter\\extract_georoc.py\"",
        "workdir": "{repo_root}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n4",
      "type": "command_task",
      "title": "1b. PetDB 筛选（规则固化）",
      "position": { "x": 340, "y": 320 },
      "params": {
        "label": "extract_petdb.py",
        "command": "\"{python_exe}\" \"{repo_root}\\01_preprocessing\\filter\\extract_petdb.py\"",
        "workdir": "{repo_root}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n5",
      "type": "command_task",
      "title": "2. 合并 GEOROC+PetDB",
      "position": { "x": 620, "y": 220 },
      "params": {
        "label": "combine_list.py",
        "command": "\"{python_exe}\" \"{repo_root}\\01_preprocessing\\combine_list.py\"",
        "workdir": "{repo_root}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n6",
      "type": "command_task",
      "title": "3. 训练/测试分层切分",
      "position": { "x": 880, "y": 220 },
      "params": {
        "label": "split_train_test.py",
        "command": "\"{python_exe}\" \"{repo_root}\\01_preprocessing\\split_train_test.py\"",
        "workdir": "{repo_root}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n7",
      "type": "command_task",
      "title": "4. 全局 RF 插补 + 缺失 mask（train fit / test transform）",
      "position": { "x": 1140, "y": 220 },
      "params": {
        "label": "imputation_train_predict.py",
        "command": "\"{python_exe}\" \"{repo_root}\\02_imputation\\imputation_train_predict.py\"",
        "workdir": "{repo_root}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n8",
      "type": "command_task",
      "title": "5. 主量无水标准化（train+test 一次跑完）",
      "position": { "x": 1400, "y": 220 },
      "params": {
        "label": "normalize_major_elements.py",
        "command": "\"{python_exe}\" \"{repo_root}\\03_normalization\\normalize_major_elements.py\"",
        "workdir": "{repo_root}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n9",
      "type": "command_task",
      "title": "6. 选择性 SMOTE（仅训练集，5 类补到 3000）",
      "position": { "x": 1660, "y": 220 },
      "params": {
        "label": "selective_smote.py",
        "command": "\"{python_exe}\" \"{repo_root}\\03_normalization\\selective_smote.py\"",
        "workdir": "{repo_root}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n10",
      "type": "command_task",
      "title": "7. 分位数分箱归一化（SMOTE 前训练集 fit→transform）",
      "position": { "x": 1920, "y": 220 },
      "params": {
        "label": "normalize.py",
        "command": "\"{python_exe}\" \"{repo_root}\\03_normalization\\normalize.py\"",
        "workdir": "{repo_root}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "n11",
      "type": "note",
      "title": "输出：最终训练集 / 测试集",
      "position": { "x": 2200, "y": 220 },
      "params": {
        "content": "产出：\n- data/06_normalized/06_normalize_basalt_train.csv（SMOTE 后）\n- data/06_normalized/06_normalize_basalt_train_no_smote.csv\n- data/06_normalized/06_normalize_basalt_test.csv\n- data/06_normalized/quantile_params.json（SMOTE 前训练集分位参数）\n- data/05_imputed/03_{train,test}_missing_mask.csv（模型第二通道）\n\n即可直接喂入 04_model/ablation_v4_vit_transformer.py（显式缺失编码训练）。所有节点均为非交互、可顺序自动执行。"
      }
    }
